* Changes in SystemC 0.2 4/3/2000

**	sc_clocks are now recognized as signal declarations.

****	Support Perl 5.005_003 and non-GCC

****	Many, Many bug fixes.


* Changes in SystemC 0.1 3/31/2000

****	Package Created


